# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file



## [Unreleased]
### Changed
- Add file handling capacity via cpp to AES encryption in C for Electronic Code Book Mode (prototyping and testing on various formats...)



## [1.0]
### Added
- Better CLI interface via flags
- Banners and ASCII art graphics

### Changed
- Bunched all operations via method pointer



## [2.0]
### Added
- Encryption / Decryption via Cipher Block Chaining Mode 
- more better banners and ASCII art
- a manpage
- a copyright

### Changed
- more flag options for CLI interface for both ecb and cbc modes and validation checks
- modified some misleading outputs
